<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Investment Approval Required</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f6f8;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 650px;
        margin: auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 25px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }

      h2 {
        color: #2f4f4f;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #333333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      ul li {
        margin: 10px 0;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #444444;
        background: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }

      ul li strong {
        color: #2f4f4f;
      }

      .cta {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 25px;
      }

      .cta a {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 22px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        background-color: #e4e3e3; /* --nav-btns-bg */
        color: #1e3a8a; /* --nav-btns-text */
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 6px;
      }

      .cta a:hover {
        background-color: rgb(234, 236, 241); /* --nav-btns-bg-hover */
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #777;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Investment Approval Required</h2>
      <p>Hello Admin,</p>
      <p>
        A new investment request has been submitted and is awaiting your
        approval. Please review the details below:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>User:</strong> {{userName}} ({{userEmail}})</li>
        <li><strong>Investment Plan:</strong> {{plan}}</li>
        <li><strong>Amount:</strong> ${{amount}}</li>
        <li><strong>Start Date:</strong> {{startDate}}</li>
        <li><strong>End Date:</strong> {{endDate}}</li>
        <li><strong>Maturity Amount:</strong> ${{maturityAmount}}</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="cta">
        <a
          href="https://www.wealthwiseportfolios.com/admin-pending-investment"
          target="_blank"
        >
          Approve or Reject Investment
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="footer">
        This is an automated message. Please log in to your admin dashboard to
        manage investments.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
